### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@host = localhost:3001

### Create User (Signup) - Success
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "formFields": [
    {
      "id": "email",
      "value": "test@example.com"
    },
    {
      "id": "password",
      "value": "testPassword123!"
    },
    {
      "id": "username",
      "value": "test_user_1"
    },
    {
      "id": "displayName",
      "value": "Test User One"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Sign In (Login) - Success
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "formFields": [
    {
      "id": "email",
      "value": "test@example.com"
    },
    {
      "id": "password",
      "value": "testPassword123!"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Sign In - Invalid Credentials
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "formFields": [
    {
      "id": "email",
      "value": "invalid@example.com"
    },
    {
      "id": "password",
      "value": "wrongpassword"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get Session - Valid Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user/session
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Session - No Token (Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user/session

###

### Sign Out
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user/signout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Health Check (No Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### API Docs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api-docs
